{"tid":423062,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想問點醫我女朋友?","createTime":"2017-10-03T15:01:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T20:52:05.000Z","uid":80011,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"48793726d897560fc4b87d9e73d2c77b870c1bb4","tid":423062,"uid":80011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T15:01:52.000Z","msg":"佢前幾日係火車定唔知邊度望到張月餅poster(唔sure係咪呢張 但係類近<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/224905_1c17e3f264813276563a6f8055d3940d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F224905_1c17e3f264813276563a6f8055d3940d.jpg&h=8142ca7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟住問我[吓 如果真係咁樣既話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁個蛋黃咪係環形囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ]<br />\n我岩岩畫左張圖, 圖示:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/225212_44c61a37292866fd1044e09ccd6aa8d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F225212_44c61a37292866fd1044e09ccd6aa8d1.jpg&h=feba899c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢係有道理 <br />\n我亦都知好多人已經諗過呢個問題<br />\n但係重點係佢問果刻真係好興奮<br />\n好似小爾雙眼發光望住我咁<br />\n我點問可以點樣制止佢<br />\n唔比佢再問啲咁難答既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04cdd3056029ed501d7027874aa96fb9432f6fc5","tid":423062,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T15:04:01.000Z","msg":"你試下合埋佢 你會發覺佢合唔到做一個月餅"},{"pid":"2d87787a165338ab524b80ebb34a85ba8e9065a2","tid":423062,"uid":64290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T15:05:23.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n我都有問過呢個問題"},{"pid":"f2e2a4f51d539a087b014ae4c3dc7c86655f9d10","tid":423062,"uid":66679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T15:07:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c2dab4915515bd3360